@node Hotlists "Hotlists"

   @{u}Hotlists@{uu}

   A hotlist is a file in wich you can save a "bookmark" to your favourite
   web-addresses so you can easily go there again whitout typing in the long
   address again.

   @{u}Where to find the hotlist file from your system:@{uu}

        @{"Netscape" link NetScape}	.netscape-bookmarks.html
        @{"NetScape2" link NetScape}	.netscape/.bookmarks.html
        @{"AMosaic" link AMosaic}	ENV:Mosaic/.
        @{"xMosaic" link xMosaic}	.mosaic-hotlist-default
        @{"Old IBrowse" link IBrowse}	Prefs/Hotlist
        @{"IBrowse" link IBrowse}	ibrowse-hotlist.html
        @{"IBrowse2" link IBrowse}	ibrowse-hotlist.html
        @{"AWeb" link AWeb}		aweb.hotlist
        @{"Voyager" link Voyager}	Bookmarks.HTML

@endnode

